comments: Wiggins (GSW) engages with Sabonis (SAC) and releases from the marginal contact as he retrieves the rebound.
Wiggins (GSW) establishes himself in Fox's (SAC) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Murray (SAC) moves slightly forward and marginal contact occurs with Curry (GSW) as they come together on the perimeter. Curry is able to move through the contact and maintain his dribble.
Looney (GSW) is firming up over his right foot in Monk's (SAC) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Barnes (SAC) straddles the lane line and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.

Replay review of the foul called on Looney (GSW) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Barnes (SAC) establishes himself as he firms up over his left foot in Looney's (GSW) path and absorbs the contact in the chest when Looney dislodges him on the shot attempt.
Wiggins (GSW) contests Fox's (SAC) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Curry (GSW) brings his hand underneath the ball and pins it to his body before he resumes his dribble thereafter.
Barnes (SAC) initiates contact with Curry's (GSW) head, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) establishes himself in Green's (GSW) path and does not deliver illegal contact during the dribble-hand-off.
Barnes (SAC) clamps and holds Looney's (GSW) arm, which affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Sabonis (SAC) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
